  <brief_title>Visual Outcome in Patients With Symptomatic Macular PCV Treated With Either Ranibizumab as Monotherapy or Combined With Verteporfin Photodynamic Therapy.</brief_title>
  <acronym>EVEREST II</acronym>
  <official_title>A 24-month, Phase IV, Randomized, Double Masked, Multi-center Study of Ranibizumab Monotherapy or Ranibizumab in Combination With Verteporfin Photodynamic Therapy on Visual Outcome in Patients With Symptomatic Macular PCV</official_title>
  <sponsors>
