  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare the effect of ranibizumab administered as monotherapy versus
      ranibizumab administered in combination with verteporfin PDT on visual acuity in patients
      with symptomatic macular PCV.  The results of this study will provide long-term safety and
      efficacy data used to generate further guidance on the management of patients with PCV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
